// TLCS Main Indicator — Changelog
// ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
//
// v2.4.3  (2026-05-31)
// ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
// FIX: Scalp Sell/Buy bounce logic correctly references all 15 S&R arrays.
//
// ROOT CAUSE:
//   The previous implementation used a single variable (`resMid` / `grsMid`) 
//   which could only remember the very last power candle's midpoint, causing 
//   it to abruptly forget valid midpoints when consecutive power candles appeared.
//
// CHANGE:
//   Removed the single `resMid` and `grsMid` variables.
//   Replaced `bouncedOffResMid` and `bouncedOffGrsMid` with helper functions 
//   that scan `sr01` through `sr15` to trigger on ANY valid line.
//
// ─── NEW TRIGGER LOGIC ───
//
// // Helper function: Check if candle perfectly rejected an S&R level
// isValidBounceDown(float srLevel) =>
//     (not na(srLevel)) and high >= srLevel and open <= srLevel and low < srLevel and close < srLevel and close < open
//
// isValidBounceUp(float srLevel) =>
//     (not na(srLevel)) and low <= srLevel and open >= srLevel and high > srLevel and close > srLevel and close > open
//
// // Check if we bounced off ANY of the 15 valid lines
// bouncedOffResMid = isValidBounceDown(sr01) or isValidBounceDown(sr02) or isValidBounceDown(sr03) or isValidBounceDown(sr04) or isValidBounceDown(sr05) or isValidBounceDown(sr06) or isValidBounceDown(sr07) or isValidBounceDown(sr08) or isValidBounceDown(sr09) or isValidBounceDown(sr10) or isValidBounceDown(sr11) or isValidBounceDown(sr12) or isValidBounceDown(sr13) or isValidBounceDown(sr14) or isValidBounceDown(sr15)
//
// bouncedOffGrsMid = isValidBounceUp(sr01) or isValidBounceUp(sr02) or isValidBounceUp(sr03) or isValidBounceUp(sr04) or isValidBounceUp(sr05) or isValidBounceUp(sr06) or isValidBounceUp(sr07) or isValidBounceUp(sr08) or isValidBounceUp(sr09) or isValidBounceUp(sr10) or isValidBounceUp(sr11) or isValidBounceUp(sr12) or isValidBounceUp(sr13) or isValidBounceUp(sr14) or isValidBounceUp(sr15)
//
// ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
